# Project Documentation

## Overview

Project documentation serves as the complete technical record of the OptiCrop development process. It captures every stage of the project, from identifying the problem to designing, developing, testing, and deploying the application. Proper documentation improves project understanding, simplifies maintenance, and provides a reference for future enhancements.

---

# Documentation Objectives

The documentation was prepared to:

- Explain the purpose and scope of the project.
- Describe the technologies and tools used.
- Record the development process.
- Document the Machine Learning workflow.
- Provide implementation and testing details.
- Support future maintenance and upgrades.

